<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>인베스트 퓨처 - 자산 관리 파트너</title>
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Manrope:wght@300;400;600;800&family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@300;400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <script>
    tailwind.config = {
      theme: {
        extend: {
          colors: {
            deepSea: '#0F172A',
            emerald: '#10B981',
            slate: '#64748B',
          },
          fontFamily: {
            display: ['Manrope', 'sans-serif'],
            sans: ['Noto Sans KR', 'sans-serif'],
          }
        }
      }
    }
  </script>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-50 text-deepSea font-sans">

  <!-- Nav -->
  <nav class="bg-white border-b border-gray-100">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 py-4 flex justify-between items-center">
      <div class="text-2xl font-display font-extrabold flex items-center gap-2 tracking-tight">
        <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-emerald" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6"></path></svg>
        InvestFuture
      </div>
      <div class="hidden md:flex gap-8 text-sm font-medium text-slate">
        <a href="#services" class="hover:text-emerald transition">상품 안내</a>
        <a href="#market" class="hover:text-emerald transition">시장 전망</a>
        <a href="#about" class="hover:text-emerald transition">회사 소개</a>
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-3">
        <button class="text-sm font-bold text-slate hover:text-deepSea">로그인</button>
        <button onclick="toggleFinance()" class="bg-deepSea text-white px-5 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm font-bold hover:bg-slate-800 transition">상담 신청</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!-- Hero with Chart Graphic -->
  <header class="py-20 px-6 container mx-auto">
    <div class="bg-deepSea text-white rounded-3xl p-12 md:p-20 relative overflow-hidden grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <!-- Background Grid -->
      <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10" style="background-image: linear-gradient(#334155 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(to right, #334155 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 40px 40px;"></div>
      
      <div class="relative z-10 space-y-6">
        <span class="text-emerald font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-xs">Smart Asset Management</span>
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-display font-extrabold leading-tight">
          Grow Your Wealth <br> with <span class="text-emerald">Confidence.</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-slate-300 text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-md">
          변동성이 큰 시장에서도 안정적인 수익을 추구합니다. <br>
          AI 기반의 데이터 분석과 전문가의 통찰력으로 당신의 자산을 지킵니다.
        </p>
        <div class="flex gap-4 pt-4">
          <button onclick="toggleFinance()" class="bg-emerald text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold hover:bg-emerald/90 transition shadow-lg shadow-emerald/20">
            포트폴리오 진단받기
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Live Chart Mockup -->
      <div class="relative z-10 bg-white/10 backdrop-blur border border-white/20 rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-2xl">
        <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-6 border-b border-white/10 pb-4">
          <div>
            <div class="text-xs text-slate-300">Total Assets</div>
            <div class="text-2xl font-bold font-display">₩ 1,245,000,000</div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-right">
            <div class="text-xs text-slate-300">Return</div>
            <div class="text-Emerald-400 font-bold text-emerald">+12.5% ↗</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Bars -->
        <div class="flex justify-between items-end h-40 gap-2">
          <div class="w-full bg-emerald/20 rounded-t h-[40%]"></div>
          <div class="w-full bg-emerald/30 rounded-t h-[30%]"></div>
          <div class="w-full bg-emerald/40 rounded-t h-[50%]"></div>
          <div class="w-full bg-emerald/50 rounded-t h-[45%]"></div>
          <div class="w-full bg-emerald/60 rounded-t h-[60%]"></div>
          <div class="w-full bg-emerald/80 rounded-t h-[75%]"></div>
          <div class="w-full bg-emerald rounded-t h-[85%] relative group">
            <div class="absolute -top-8 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 bg-white text-deepSea text-xs font-bold px-2 py-1 rounded shadow opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition">Today</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- Products -->
  <section id="services" class="py-20 px-6 container mx-auto">
    <div class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-display font-bold mb-4">투자 상품</h2>
      <p class="text-slate">고객의 성향에 맞춘 최적의 포트폴리오를 제안합니다.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <!-- Card 1 -->
      <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl hover:border-emerald transition duration-300 group cursor-pointer" onclick="toggleFinance()">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-50 text-blue-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">🛡️</div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-deepSea">안정형 펀드</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate leading-relaxed mb-6">
          채권 및 국공채 위주의 포트폴리오로 원금 손실 위험을 최소화합니다.
        </p>
        <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-600 mb-1">연 4.5%</div>
        <div class="text-xs text-slate">예상 수익률</div>
      </div>
      <!-- Card 2 -->
      <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl hover:border-emerald transition duration-300 group cursor-pointer" onclick="toggleFinance()">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-emerald-50 text-emerald rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">📈</div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-deepSea">밸런스 펀드</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate leading-relaxed mb-6">
          주식과 채권의 적절한 배분을 통해 안정성과 수익성을 동시에 추구합니다.
        </p>
        <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-emerald mb-1">연 8.2%</div>
        <div class="text-xs text-slate">예상 수익률</div>
      </div>
      <!-- Card 3 -->
      <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl hover:border-emerald transition duration-300 group cursor-pointer" onclick="toggleFinance()">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-purple-50 text-purple-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">🚀</div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-deepSea">성장형 펀드</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate leading-relaxed mb-6">
          미래 유망 산업과 기술주에 집중 투자하여 높은 수익을 목표로 합니다.
        </p>
        <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-purple-600 mb-1">연 15.0%+</div>
        <div class="text-xs text-slate">예상 수익률</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gray-100">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-display font-bold mb-6">투자의 시작, 전문가와 함께하세요</h2>
      <button onclick="toggleFinance()" class="bg-white text-deepSea px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold border border-gray-200 hover:border-emerald hover:text-emerald transition shadow-sm">
        무료 투자 성향 분석
      </button>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Modal -->
  <div id="finance-modal" class="fixed inset-0 bg-deepSea/80 z-[60] hidden flex items-center justify-center p-4">
    <div class="bg-white w-full max-w-lg rounded-2xl p-10 relative shadow-2xl">
      <button onclick="toggleFinance()" class="absolute top-4 right-4 text-gray-400 hover:text-deepSea">&times;</button>
      
      <div class="text-center mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-deepSea mb-2">Consultation Request</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate">전문 PB가 1:1 맞춤 상담을 도와드립니다.</p>
      </div>

      <form class="space-y-4" onsubmit="event.preventDefault(); alert('상담 신청이 완료되었습니다. 24시간 내로 연락드리겠습니다.'); toggleFinance();">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
           <input type="text" placeholder="성함" class="w-full bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 p-3 rounded-lg outline-none focus:border-emerald text-sm text-deepSea">
           <input type="tel" placeholder="연락처" class="w-full bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 p-3 rounded-lg outline-none focus:border-emerald text-sm text-deepSea">
        </div>
        <input type="text" placeholder="투자 가능 금액 (예: 1억원)" class="w-full bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 p-3 rounded-lg outline-none focus:border-emerald text-sm text-deepSea">
        <select class="w-full bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 p-3 rounded-lg outline-none focus:border-emerald text-sm text-slate">
          <option>투자 목표 선택</option>
          <option>노후 자금 마련</option>
          <option>주택 마련</option>
          <option>자녀 학자금</option>
          <option>단기 자금 운용</option>
        </select>
        <textarea rows="3" placeholder="기타 문의사항" class="w-full bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 p-3 rounded-lg outline-none focus:border-emerald text-sm text-deepSea resize-none"></textarea>
        
        <button class="w-full bg-emerald text-white font-bold py-4 rounded-lg hover:bg-emerald/90 transition shadow-lg mt-2">
          신청하기
        </button>
      </form>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script>
    function toggleFinance() {
      const modal = document.getElementById('finance-modal');
      if(modal.classList.contains('hidden')) {
        modal.classList.remove('hidden');
      } else {
        modal.classList.add('hidden');
      }
    }
  </script>
</body>
</html>
